name: HOMELESS-MAN
description:
Homeless-man !!!
Part of Depression Art !!!
.
Homelessness is lacking stable and appropriate housing. People can be categorized as homeless if they are: living on the streets (primary homelessness); moving between temporary shelters, including houses of friends, family and emergency accommodation (secondary homelessness); living in private boarding houses without a private bathroom or security of tenure (tertiary homelessness). The purpose of creating this art is to educated people about homelessness.
